Would you like to see Meghan Markle run for US President? Have your say

Terminator star turned politician Arnold Schwarzenegger trained as a bodybuilder before finding fame as a Hollywood action hero, most famously in the Terminator series. He later served two terms as Governor of California, from 2003 to 2011. In 2011 Schwarzenegger separated from his wife of 25 years Maria Shriver, after it was revealed he had fathered a son 14 years earlier with their housekeeper.
